<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>500 — Erreur serveur · La Pizza d'Ischia</title>
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Instrument+Serif:ital@0;1&family=Manrope:wght@300;400;500&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
        <style>
            *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

            :root {
                --ink:       #1a1410;
                --paper:     #f3ece0;
                --gold:      #b8893a;
                --tomato:    #c54328;
                --line:      rgb(243 236 224 / 10%);
                --font-display: "Instrument Serif", Georgia, serif;
                --font-body:    "Manrope", system-ui, sans-serif;
                --font-mono:    "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
            }

            html, body { height: 100%; }

            body {
                background-color: var(--ink);
                color: var(--paper);
                font-family: var(--font-body);
                min-height: 100svh;
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .topbar {
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 2.5rem;
                padding: 0 3rem;
                height: 72px;
                border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
                flex-shrink: 0;
            }

            .topbar-item {
                font-family: var(--font-mono);
                font-size: 0.62rem;
                font-weight: 500;
                letter-spacing: 0.22em;
                text-transform: uppercase;
                color: rgb(243 236 224 / 35%);
            }

            .topbar-item + .topbar-item {
                padding-left: 2.5rem;
                border-left: 1px solid var(--line);
            }

            .main {
                flex: 1;
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                justify-content: flex-end;
                padding: 4rem 3rem 5rem;
                gap: 3rem;
            }

            .error-code {
                font-family: var(--font-display);
                font-size: clamp(120px, 22vw, 320px);
                font-weight: 400;
                font-style: italic;
                line-height: 0.85;
                letter-spacing: -0.04em;
                color: var(--gold);
            }

            .error-body {
                display: grid;
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
                gap: 3rem;
                max-width: 900px;
            }

            .error-title {
                font-family: var(--font-display);
                font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2vw, 1.8rem);
                font-weight: 400;
                line-height: 1.3;
                color: var(--paper);
            }

            .error-title em {
                font-style: italic;
                color: rgb(243 236 224 / 55%);
            }

            .error-desc {
                font-size: 0.88rem;
                font-weight: 300;
                color: rgb(243 236 224 / 45%);
                line-height: 1.8;
            }

            .error-ctas {
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 1.5rem;
                flex-wrap: wrap;
            }

            .btn-primary {
                display: inline-flex;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 0.5rem;
                background-color: var(--tomato);
                color: var(--paper);
                text-decoration: none;
                padding: 0.9rem 2rem;
                font-family: var(--font-mono);
                font-size: 0.65rem;
                font-weight: 500;
                letter-spacing: 0.2em;
                text-transform: uppercase;
                transition: background-color 0.25s ease;
            }

            .btn-primary:hover { background-color: #a8371f; }

            @media (width <= 768px) {
                .topbar { padding: 0 1.5rem; gap: 1rem; }
                .topbar-item:nth-child(3) { display: none; }
                .main { padding: 3rem 1.5rem 4rem; }
                .error-body { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; }
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>

        <div class="topbar">
            <span class="topbar-item">— Erreur 500</span>
            <span class="topbar-item">Problème serveur</span>
            <span class="topbar-item">La Pizza d'Ischia</span>
        </div>

        <main class="main">

            <span class="error-code">500.</span>

            <div class="error-body">
                <h1 class="error-title">
                    Quelque chose<br>a <em>mal tourné</em><br>de notre côté.
                </h1>
                <p class="error-desc">
                    Le serveur a rencontré une erreur inattendue. Ce n'est pas de votre faute.<br><br>
                    Réessayez dans quelques instants. Si le problème persiste, le four, lui, fonctionne toujours.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="error-ctas">
                <a href="/" class="btn-primary">Retour à l'accueil &rarr;</a>
            </div>

        </main>

    </body>
</html>
